$ 距离为 0.4 ，有个圆形通道经过 $E ， F$ ，且与 $A D$ 只有一个交点，求圆形通道的周长 $\\qquad$ . (精确到 $0.01)$\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-118.jpg?height=318&width=304&top__y=889&top__x=299","line":2324},{"title":"|401x429","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-161.jpg?height=429&width=401&top__y=982&top__x=468","line":3169,"embedded":true},{"title":"50,60$ ) 内的人数为 16 ，则下列结论正确的是（）\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-185.jpg?height=435&width=618&top__y=1781&top__x=296","line":3666}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"19gd1oy","at":1771320760602}},"smart_blocks:01-数学教学/讲义/09-讲义汇总/XDF讲义/FY25 高三数学秋季【行远班教材】3.0.md#目录": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.05193528,-0.00620755,0.0640782,-0.00106329,0.02578065,-0.01246565,-0.05027597,0.02108635,0.03339488,0.05474157,0.01549845,-0.05922662,0.03766235,0.00749742,0.002152,-0.00525272,-0.00988233,-0.03777747,-0.04084071,-0.01989747,0.13168107,-0.02168059,-0.01122145,-0.05674368,0.06361325,0.04205979,0.01028959,-0.06795824,-0.0267465,-0.1967423,-0.01331206,0.07899669,0.06819584,0.02469651,0.04926863,-0.04331677,-0.01128173,0.07394556,-0.01675167,0.0582914,0.00245688,0.07670904,-0.00289132,0.00832876,0.00325483,-0.08156843,-0.02794648,-0.02618325,0.03068308,-0.04574599,-0.0276634,-0.0406282,0.00637037,0.04527114,-0.0173887,0.00483258,0.05538483,0.0218497,0.0053117,0.010436,0.00724826,0.00260571,-0.23452942,0.05531782,0.06347329,-0.03143223,-0.0239039,-0.03296372,0.02477313,0.07189012,-0.04062274,-0.01980538,-0.00122423,-0.00032361,-0.01519904,-0.030566,0.00119911,-0.09193536,-0.01342654,-0.07692233,-0.00389479,0.09949369,-0.03724187,-0.01254906,0.00157448,0.02913202,0.00057784,-0.08924337,-0.01075685,-0.03896895,0.00729034,-0.02682821,-0.00645776,0.02235075,-0.06902515,-0.03207354,0.00253742,0.02376534,-0.02210441,0.08321409,-0.0435068,0.02375446,0.04623358,0.00448359,-0